OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FA small school district in America has
OL,7,Fbeen paid $27 million (around #20
OL,8,Fmillion) by a group of social media
OL,9,Fcompanies, after arguing their
OL,10,Fproducts were responsible for damaging
OL,11,Fpupils' mental health.
OL,13,FMeta, which owns Facebook and
OL,14,FInstagram, chose to pay the settlement
OL,15,Fthis week rather than defend itself in
OL,16,Fa Californian court.
OL,18,FThe tech giant faced claims its social
OL,19,Fnetwork was deliberately designed to
OL,20,Fbe addictive, causing harm to children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FTik Tok, Snap and YouTube had already
OL,7,Fchosen to settle, contributing to the
OL,8,Fpayout. All four tech giants deny any
OL,9,Fwrongdoing.
OL,11,FBreathitt School District, which looks
OL,12,Fafter six schools in Kentucky, sued
OL,13,Fthe companies to fund specialist
OL,14,Fmental health support for pupils
OL,15,Fsuffering from depression and anxiety.
OL,17,FIts claim was viewed as a bellwether
OL,18,Fcase by other far larger US school
OL,19,Fdistricts, such as Los Angeles and New
OL,20,FYork, who are already planning to sue
OL,21,Ffor much bigger sums.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
