CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson for Meta
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've resolved this case
OL,8,Famicably and remain focused on our
OL,9,Flongstanding work to build protections
OL,10,Flike Teen Accounts, that help teens
OL,11,Fstay safe online while giving parents
OL,12,Fsimple controls to support their
OL,13,Ffamilies."
OL,15,FIt came just weeks after the company's
OL,16,Fowner Mark Zuckerberg had to give
OL,17,Fevidence in a similar trial in Los
OL,18,FAngeles, alongside representatives
OL,19,Ffrom YouTube.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FThe two companies had to pay out $6
OL,7,Fmillion (around #4.5 million) to a
OL,8,Fyoung woman after the jury found they
OL,9,Fhad deliberately designed addictive
OL,10,Fproducts and failed to provide
OL,11,Fadequate warnings about their safety.
OL,13,FSnap and TikTok were also named in the
OL,14,Fcase but settled before the trial.
OL,15,FBoth YouTube and Meta have said they
OL,16,Fplan to appeal the rulings.
OL,18,FCould the same happen in the UK?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
