OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FTeachers in the UK share similar
OL,7,Fconcerns about the harm social media
OL,8,Fis causing their pupils. Many schools
OL,9,Fare trying to combat it by putting
OL,10,Ftougher limits on the access children
OL,11,Fhave to their devices.
OL,13,FBut at Ecclesfield School in Sheffield
OL,14,Fthey are in no doubt about the extra
OL,15,Fcosts they face, on both a financial
OL,16,Fand emotional level.
OL,18,FLiz Hunter, curriculum leader of PHSE
OL,19,Fand RE at the school, describes a
OL,20,Flitany of mental health problems her
OL,21,Fteam deals with every day
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
