OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FTeacher Liz Hunter tells how she sees
OL,7,Fsocial media affecting the mental
OL,8,Fhealth of her school's pupils
OL,10,FWhen I ask her how many of those
OL,11,Fproblems are caused by social media
OL,12,Fshe is adamant.
OL,14,F'Almost all of them' she sighs.
OL,16,FSo could teachers in the UK follow the
OL,17,FAmerican example and try to win back
OL,18,Fany costs to their schools through the
OL,19,Fcourts?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
