OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FThe British state school system is
OL,7,Fcentrally funded and regulated making
OL,8,Fit very different to its more
OL,9,Findependent and localised American
OL,10,Fcounterpart.
OL,12,FUK legal experts warn the British
OL,13,Fjudicial system is also far less
OL,14,Ffavourable, as Heather Gagen, head of
OL,15,Fdispute resolution at London law firm
OL,16,FTravers Smith explains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,F"There is a long history of product
OL,7,Frelated litigation that's novel,
OL,8,Ftracking across the Atlantic from the
OL,9,FUS to the UK. But how those claims
OL,10,Factually play out in practice can look
OL,11,Fvery different," she told ITV News.
OL,13,FTravers Smith LLP's Heather Gagen
OL,14,Fexplains how fundamental differences
OL,15,Fbetween the English and US legal
OL,16,Fsystems could prove an obstacle for
OL,17,Fwould-be claimants
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FBig Tech is certainly under scrutiny
OL,7,Fhere for the duties that it owes its
OL,8,Fyounger users, but I think the open
OL,9,Fquestion is, is it going to be
OL,10,Fpolicymakers who are actively looking
OL,11,Fat this area or litigation that
OL,12,Fdefines the scope of those duties?
OL,14,F"There are also differences in English
OL,15,Flaw and US law that would be relevant
OL,16,Fto these claims, but importantly,
OL,17,Fthere are differences in the legal
OL,18,Fprocess.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,F"So in England, it is judges, not
OL,7,Fjuries, who make awards of
OL,8,Fcompensation, and that tends to mean
OL,9,Fthat we see higher levels of award in
OL,10,Fthe US than we would in the UK.
OL,12,F"Cost rules here are also different,
OL,13,Fand I think those are the sorts of
OL,14,Ffactors that would play into different
OL,15,Flitigation and settlement strategies
OL,16,Fpotentially here.
OL,18,F"So, in short, while it's possible
OL,19,Fthese claims could be made here, they
OL,20,Fwould be by no means straightforward
OL,21,Fto bring or to win."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
