OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FInstead, the British government is
OL,7,Fleaning towards introducing more
OL,8,Fsweeping laws to take on the tech
OL,9,Fgiants, forcing them to change their
OL,10,Fbehaviour or face huge fines.
OL,12,FThe Online Safety Act aims to achieve
OL,13,Fthis ` placing new legal duties on
OL,14,Fplatforms to protect children from
OL,15,Fharmful content, while giving
OL,16,Fregulator Ofcom the power to imposed
OL,17,Ffines of up to #18 million, or 10% of
OL,18,Fglobal annual turnover, for non-
OL,19,Fcompliance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
