CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780229466
OL,3,CAmerican schools win $20m payout from
OL,4,Csocial media companies
OL,6,FBut like the cases against big tobacco
OL,7,Fin the 1990s, which focused on
OL,8,Fcigarettes addictive qualities and
OL,9,Fcompanies' public denials, the tech
OL,10,Fcompanies that wanted our likes are
OL,11,Fnow facing a growing wave of legal
OL,12,Faction.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
